{# 

Options for user selectable styling 
Various changes in style are applied by adding classes to the main outer site-hero container:
<<< Add the class on the left to have the effect on the right >>>

    Brand circles opacity:

    no class (default)  =   50%
    brand-opacity25     =   25% opacity
    brand-opacity50     =   50% opacity
    brand-opacity75     =   75% opacity
    brand-opacity100    =   100% opacity


    Brand circles position/orientation:

    default (no class)  =   top left
    brand-topleft       =   top left
    brand-topright      =   top right
    brand-bottomleft    =   bottom left
    brand-bottomright   =   bottom right


    Brand Circles colour:
    
    default (no class)  =   site accent colour
    brand-colour-site   =   site accent colour
    brand-colour-white  =   white
    brand-colour-black  =   black


 #}


